  "texts": [
    "The utilization of AI to analyze real-time consumer feedback will enable companies to respond swiftly to market dynamics and develop flavor products that resonate with evolving consumer preferences.",
    "This agility in product development is crucial in an era where consumer tastes are constantly shifting, driven by trends in health, wellness, and lifestyle.",
    "Moreover, integrating social media trend analysis with AI can provide brands with deeper insights into consumer behavior, allowing them to refine their marketing strategies and achieve precise market positioning.",
    "By understanding the nuances of consumer sentiment expressed online, brands can tailor their messaging and product offerings to better align with the expectations of their target audiences.",
    "Several AI-based olfactory and gustatory systems have already been translated into realworld applications, particularly in food innovation and quality monitoring."
